{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":846,"text":"The world is changing"},{"time":2149,"text":"in some really profound ways,"},{"time":4861,"text":"and I worry that investors"},{"time":6844,"text":"aren't paying enough attention"},{"time":8578,"text":"to some of the biggest drivers of change,"},{"time":10443,"text":"especially when it comes to sustainability."},{"time":14219,"text":"And by sustainability, I mean the really juicy things,"},{"time":17674,"text":"like environmental and social issues"},{"time":19577,"text":"and corporate governance."},{"time":22086,"text":"I think it's reckless to ignore these things,"},{"time":24352,"text":"because doing so can jeopardize"},{"time":25998,"text":"future long-term returns."},{"time":28467,"text":"And here's something that may surprise you:"},{"time":30663,"text":"the balance of power to really influence sustainability"},{"time":35334,"text":"rests with institutional investors,"},{"time":37489,"text":"the large investors like pension funds,"},{"time":40525,"text":"foundations and endowments."},{"time":43481,"text":"I believe that sustainable investing"},{"time":45075,"text":"is less complicated than you think,"},{"time":47725,"text":"better-performing than you believe,"},{"time":49753,"text":"and more important than we can imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52626,"text":"Let me remind you what we already know."},{"time":55634,"text":"We have a population that's both growing and aging;"},{"time":59180,"text":"we have seven billion souls today"},{"time":61026,"text":"heading to 10 billion"},{"time":62452,"text":"at the end of the century;"},{"time":64353,"text":"we consume natural resources"},{"time":66851,"text":"faster than they can be replenished;"},{"time":69677,"text":"and the emissions that are mainly responsible"},{"time":72114,"text":"for climate change just keep increasing."},{"time":76943,"text":"Now clearly, these are\nenvironmental and social issues,"},{"time":81160,"text":"but that's not all."},{"time":83092,"text":"They're economic issues,"},{"time":85064,"text":"and that makes them relevant"},{"time":86800,"text":"to risk and return."},{"time":90077,"text":"And they are really complex"},{"time":92157,"text":"and they can seem really far off,"},{"time":93822,"text":"that the temptation may be to do this:"},{"time":97108,"text":"bury our heads in the sand and not think about it."},{"time":100474,"text":"Resist this, if you can. Don't do this at home."},{"time":103124,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105050,"text":"But it makes me wonder"},{"time":106693,"text":"if the investment rules of today"},{"time":108706,"text":"are fit for purpose tomorrow."},{"time":111951,"text":"We know that investors,"},{"time":113789,"text":"when they look at a company\nand decide whether to invest,"},{"time":116649,"text":"they look at financial data,"},{"time":118281,"text":"metrics like sales growth, cash flow, market share,"},{"time":122301,"text":"valuation -- you know, the really sexy stuff."},{"time":127713,"text":"And these things are fundamental, of course,"},{"time":130040,"text":"but they're not enough."},{"time":131805,"text":"Investors should also look at performance metrics"},{"time":134254,"text":"in what we call ESG:"},{"time":136178,"text":"environment, social and governance."},{"time":139020,"text":"Environment includes energy consumption,"},{"time":143782,"text":"water availability, waste and pollution,"},{"time":149166,"text":"just making efficient uses of resources."},{"time":152985,"text":"Social includes human capital,"},{"time":155112,"text":"things like employee engagement"},{"time":156980,"text":"and innovation capacity,"},{"time":159324,"text":"as well as supply chain management"},{"time":162636,"text":"and labor rights and human rights."},{"time":166206,"text":"And governance relates to the oversight"},{"time":168014,"text":"of companies by their boards and investors."},{"time":171795,"text":"See, I told you this is the really juicy stuff."},{"time":174906,"text":"But ESG is the measure of sustainability,"},{"time":179093,"text":"and sustainable investing incorporates ESG factors"},{"time":183234,"text":"with financial factors into the investment process."},{"time":187351,"text":"It means limiting future risk"},{"time":189479,"text":"by minimizing harm to people and planet,"},{"time":193088,"text":"and it means providing capital to users"},{"time":196703,"text":"who deploy it towards productive"},{"time":198863,"text":"and sustainable outcomes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201587,"text":"So if sustainability matters financially today,"},{"time":204751,"text":"and all signs indicate more tomorrow,"},{"time":207243,"text":"is the private sector paying attention?"},{"time":210741,"text":"Well, the really cool thing is that most CEOs are."},{"time":216722,"text":"They started to see sustainability"},{"time":218288,"text":"not just as important but crucial to business success."},{"time":222532,"text":"About 80 percent of global CEOs"},{"time":224946,"text":"see sustainability as the root to growth in innovation"},{"time":229037,"text":"and leading to competitive advantage"},{"time":231430,"text":"in their industries."},{"time":233154,"text":"But 93 percent see ESG as the future,"},{"time":236327,"text":"or as important to the future of their business."},{"time":239376,"text":"So the views of CEOs are clear."},{"time":242593,"text":"There's tremendous opportunity in sustainability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245780,"text":"So how are companies actually leveraging ESG"},{"time":249308,"text":"to drive hard business results?"},{"time":252110,"text":"One example is near and dear to our hearts."},{"time":254631,"text":"In 2012, State Street migrated 54 applications"},{"time":258065,"text":"to the cloud environment,"},{"time":259711,"text":"and we retired another 85."},{"time":262140,"text":"We virtualized our operating system environments,"},{"time":264846,"text":"and we completed numerous automation projects."},{"time":268309,"text":"Now these initiatives create\na more mobile workplace,"},{"time":270841,"text":"and they reduce our real estate footprint,"},{"time":273625,"text":"and they yield savings of 23 million dollars"},{"time":276265,"text":"in operating costs annually,"},{"time":279265,"text":"and avoid the emissions"},{"time":281101,"text":"of a 100,000 metric tons of carbon."},{"time":285551,"text":"That's the equivalent of taking 21,000 cars"},{"time":288584,"text":"off the road."},{"time":290373,"text":"So awesome, right?"},{"time":293012,"text":"Another example is Pentair."},{"time":295976,"text":"Pentair is a U.S. industrial conglomerate,"},{"time":298305,"text":"and about a decade ago,"},{"time":299885,"text":"they sold their core power tools business"},{"time":302372,"text":"and reinvested those proceeds in a water business."},{"time":306630,"text":"That's a really big bet. Why did they do that?"},{"time":310593,"text":"Well, with apologies to the Home Improvement fans,"},{"time":313321,"text":"there's more growth in water than in power tools,"},{"time":316243,"text":"and this company has their sights set"},{"time":318165,"text":"on what they call \"the new New World.\""},{"time":320532,"text":"That's four billion middle class people"},{"time":322915,"text":"demanding food, energy and water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328069,"text":"Now, you may be asking yourself,"},{"time":331193,"text":"are these just isolated cases?"},{"time":332859,"text":"I mean, come on, really?"},{"time":334837,"text":"Do companies that take sustainability into account"},{"time":336846,"text":"really do well financially?"},{"time":339032,"text":"The answer that may surprise you is yes."},{"time":341878,"text":"The data shows that stocks\nwith better ESG performance"},{"time":345043,"text":"perform just as well as others."},{"time":348390,"text":"In blue, we see the MSCI World."},{"time":350664,"text":"It's an index of large companies"},{"time":352101,"text":"from developed markets across the world."},{"time":354890,"text":"And in gold, we see a subset of companies"},{"time":357362,"text":"rated as having the best ESG performance."},{"time":360145,"text":"Over three plus years, no performance tradeoff."},{"time":364396,"text":"So that's okay, right? We want more. I want more."},{"time":368807,"text":"In some cases, there may be outperformance"},{"time":371370,"text":"from ESG."},{"time":373953,"text":"In blue, we see the performance"},{"time":376131,"text":"of the 500 largest global companies,"},{"time":378546,"text":"and in gold, we see a subset of companies"},{"time":381859,"text":"with best practice in climate change strategy"},{"time":384682,"text":"and risk management."},{"time":386115,"text":"Now over almost eight years,"},{"time":387545,"text":"they've outperformed by about two thirds."},{"time":390555,"text":"So yes, this is correlation. It's not causation."},{"time":394449,"text":"But it does illustrate that environmental leadership"},{"time":396978,"text":"is compatible with good returns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400051,"text":"So if the returns are the same or better"},{"time":404394,"text":"and the planet benefits, wouldn't this be the norm?"},{"time":407505,"text":"Are investors, particularly institutional investors,"},{"time":410636,"text":"engaged?"},{"time":412075,"text":"Well, some are,"},{"time":413952,"text":"and a few are really at the vanguard."},{"time":417288,"text":"Hesta."},{"time":418527,"text":"Hesta is a retirement fund for health"},{"time":420774,"text":"and community services employees in Australia,"},{"time":423469,"text":"with assets of 22 billion [dollars]."},{"time":425714,"text":"They believe that ESG has the potential"},{"time":427537,"text":"to impact risks and returns,"},{"time":429605,"text":"so incorporating it into the investment process"},{"time":432897,"text":"is core to their duty"},{"time":435113,"text":"to act in the best interest of fund members,"},{"time":437271,"text":"core to their duty."},{"time":438957,"text":"You gotta love the Aussies, right?"},{"time":442668,"text":"CalPERS is another example."},{"time":445176,"text":"CalPERS is the pension fund"},{"time":447197,"text":"for public employees in California,"},{"time":449478,"text":"and with assets of 244 billion [dollars],"},{"time":452194,"text":"they are the second largest in the U.S."},{"time":454286,"text":"and the sixth largest in the world."},{"time":456983,"text":"Now, they're moving toward 100 percent"},{"time":458546,"text":"sustainable investment"},{"time":460135,"text":"by systematically integrated ESG"},{"time":462217,"text":"across the entire fund."},{"time":464966,"text":"Why? They believe it's critical"},{"time":468423,"text":"to superior long-term returns, full stop."},{"time":472954,"text":"In their own words, \"long-term value creation"},{"time":475546,"text":"requires the effective management"},{"time":477586,"text":"of three forms of capital:"},{"time":479728,"text":"financial, human, and physical."},{"time":484447,"text":"This is why we are concerned with ESG.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":488306,"text":"Now, I do speak to a lot of investors"},{"time":490714,"text":"as part of my job,"},{"time":492441,"text":"and not all of them see it this way."},{"time":494735,"text":"Often I hear, \"We are required to maximize returns,"},{"time":498493,"text":"so we don't do that here,\""},{"time":500243,"text":"or, \"We don't want to use the portfolio"},{"time":502590,"text":"to make policy statements.\""},{"time":505094,"text":"The one that just really gets under my skin is,"},{"time":507960,"text":"\"If you want to do something about that,"},{"time":510012,"text":"just make money, give the profits to charities.\""},{"time":513475,"text":"It's eyes rolling, eyes rolling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517244,"text":"I mean, let me clarify something right here."},{"time":521267,"text":"Companies and investors are not"},{"time":523872,"text":"singularly responsible for the fate of the planet."},{"time":526631,"text":"They don't have indefinite social obligations,"},{"time":529019,"text":"and prudent investing and finance theory"},{"time":531792,"text":"aren't subordinate to sustainability."},{"time":533891,"text":"They're compatible."},{"time":535547,"text":"So I'm not talking about tradeoffs here."},{"time":540012,"text":"But institutional investors"},{"time":541989,"text":"are the x-factor in sustainability."},{"time":545155,"text":"Why do they hold the key?"},{"time":547218,"text":"The answer, quite simply, is, they have the money."},{"time":550933,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":553619,"text":"A lot of it."},{"time":556015,"text":"I mean, a really lot of it."},{"time":557757,"text":"The global stock market is worth 55 trillion dollars."},{"time":560600,"text":"The global bond market, 78 trillion."},{"time":563658,"text":"That's 133 trillion combined."},{"time":568836,"text":"That's eight and a half times the GDP of the U.S."},{"time":571507,"text":"That's the world's largest economy."},{"time":573726,"text":"That's some serious freaking firepower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577563,"text":"So we can reconsider"},{"time":579612,"text":"some of these pressing challenges,"},{"time":581535,"text":"like fresh water, clean air,"},{"time":584049,"text":"feeding 10 billion mouths,"},{"time":586074,"text":"if institutional investors"},{"time":587751,"text":"integrated ESG into investment."},{"time":590163,"text":"What if they used that firepower"},{"time":592314,"text":"to allocate more of their capital"},{"time":594358,"text":"to companies working the hardest"},{"time":595771,"text":"at solving these challenges"},{"time":597853,"text":"or at least not exacerbating them?"},{"time":600969,"text":"What if we work and save and invest,"},{"time":605806,"text":"only to find that the world we retire into"},{"time":608439,"text":"is more stressed and less secure than it is now?"},{"time":612165,"text":"What if there isn't enough clean air and fresh water?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617037,"text":"Now a fair question might be,"},{"time":619525,"text":"what if all this sustainability risk stuff"},{"time":621421,"text":"is exaggerated, overstated, it's not urgent,"},{"time":625957,"text":"something for virtuous consumers"},{"time":628110,"text":"or lifestyle choice?"},{"time":630066,"text":"Well, President John F. Kennedy said something"},{"time":632805,"text":"about this that is just spot on:"},{"time":636290,"text":"\"There are risks and costs to a program of action,"},{"time":640102,"text":"but they are far less than the long-range risks"},{"time":642751,"text":"and costs of comfortable inaction.\""},{"time":647366,"text":"I can appreciate that there is estimation risk in this,"},{"time":650984,"text":"but since this is based on\nwidespread scientific consensus,"},{"time":654619,"text":"the odds that it's not completely wrong"},{"time":657180,"text":"are better than the odds"},{"time":658796,"text":"that our house will burn down"},{"time":660471,"text":"or we'll get in a car accident."},{"time":662406,"text":"Well, maybe not if you live in Boston. (Laughter)"},{"time":666000,"text":"But my point is that we buy insurance"},{"time":669303,"text":"to protect ourselves financially"},{"time":671286,"text":"in case those things happen, right?"},{"time":674489,"text":"So by investing sustainably"},{"time":676038,"text":"we're doing two things."},{"time":678257,"text":"We're creating insurance,"},{"time":680415,"text":"reducing the risk to our planet and to our economy,"},{"time":684661,"text":"and at the same time, in the short term,"},{"time":686650,"text":"we're not sacrificing performance."},{"time":689326,"text":"[Man in comic: \"What if it's a big hoax \nand we create a better world for nothing?\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":694083,"text":"Good, you like it. I like it too."},{"time":696199,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":697776,"text":"I like it because it pokes fun"},{"time":699849,"text":"at both sides of the climate change issue."},{"time":702444,"text":"I bet you can't guess which side I'm on."},{"time":705788,"text":"But what I really like about it"},{"time":707527,"text":"is that it reminds me of something Mark Twain said,"},{"time":710456,"text":"which is, \"Plan for the future,"},{"time":712525,"text":"because that's where you're going to spend"},{"time":714095,"text":"the rest of your life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":716596,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718955,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}